title: Branko Gračanin
text: Branko Gračanin (born 19 October 1943 in <a href="Zagreb">Zagreb</a>, <a href="Kingdom%20of%20Yugoslavia">Kingdom of Yugoslavia</a>) is a former Croatian <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player. He capped 10 times, scoring 1 goal for <a href="Yugoslavia%20national%20football%20team">Yugoslavia</a>.
